name: Jquery-streetfighter
body:
### jQuery Streetfighter Project
Working with Animated Gifs, and jQuery to Show and Hide different files in the frame.  Chaining Animation to the mousedown event to execute the fireball shot from the hands.  

### Authors and Contributors
2015 Michelle Burton (@cyandream), working on Thinkful files.
